# EmailJS Configuration
# Get your Public Key from: https://dashboard.emailjs.com/account
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here

# You'll also need to set up the following in EmailJS:
# 1. Create a free account at https://www.emailjs.com/
# 2. Add a Service (Gmail recommended)
# 3. Create an Email Template with:
#    - Service ID: service_dark_canvas
#    - Template ID: template_contact_form
#    - Template variables: from_name, from_email, subject, message, to_email
# 4. Copy your Public Key and paste it below as VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY
